{"tid":806276,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩篇新聞咁似，係咪我多心","createTime":"2018-09-04T13:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T14:06:25.000Z","uid":203889,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"74d76c9906ee517ab400981a868ae7aa52ad8a13","tid":806276,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T13:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 岩岩做功課搵料既時候見到<br />\n係咪我多心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定份份報紙其實都係咁寫<br />\n<br />\n紅底01 2018-05-12<br />\n不過，公務員設有「跳point」制度，即當未達到頂薪點，每年可增加一個薪級點，故政府在計算加薪指標時，會先扣減公務員遞增薪額開支，避免雙重加薪。今年低層公務員需扣減2.05%遞增薪額，較去年高出0.09%，增幅比率為歷年新高，而中層及高層公務員需扣減的遞增薪額亦創新高。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/政情/187472/公務員加薪-下周公布-遞增薪點扣減率創新高-會否少加人工\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85%2F187472%2F%E5%85%AC%E5%8B%99%E5%93%A1%E5%8A%A0%E8%96%AA-%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83-%E9%81%9E%E5%A2%9E%E8%96%AA%E9%BB%9E%E6%89%A3%E6%B8%9B%E7%8E%87%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-%E6%9C%83%E5%90%A6%E5%B0%91%E5%8A%A0%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5&d=Pm1Q8Wns8gYR5VKS1fMOpFKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=62b9b850\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/政情/187472/公務員加薪-下周公布-遞增薪點扣減率創新高-會否少加人工</a><br />\n<br />\n2017-05-18 蘋果<br />\n公務員設有跳point制度，若未到頂薪點，每年可增加一個薪級點，因此政府在計算加薪指標時，會先扣減公務員遞增薪額開支，避免雙重加薪。今年低層公務員需扣減1.96%遞增薪額，比率是歷年新高，而中層及高層公務員需扣減的遞增薪額則是回歸後新高。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20170518/56710425\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170518%2F56710425&d=Pm1Q8Wns8gYR5VKS1fMOpFKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=fa95a2a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170518%2F56710425&h=81a2099e\" 